Digital board (ACE-00711) Rev F. pattern files are based on P06B97_3A.txt but with
different vertical shift patterns. CMM (11/6/07)
(uses faster 12.5ns engine clock with C5 polo and discrete dig b/d)
2 phase device with I1=I2, I3=I4, S1=S2, S3=S4
For iXon 97BI Datel ADS937 1MHz 16bit A/D with EM and conventional outputs.
Important for horz clks to have 90% overlap, if not done in pattern then in verniers.
